name: MySQL5
queryCode:
SELECT
	t1.ID,t1.`case`,t1.VERSION,CONCAT('#',t1.VERSION) as expect
FROM
	(
SELECT
	t1.`ID`,
	t1.`CASE`,
	t1.`VERSION` 
FROM
	`zt_casestep` t1 where t1.version <> 1 
GROUP BY
	t1.`CASE`,
	t1.`VERSION` UNION ALL
SELECT
	1 AS ID,
	t1.`id` AS `CASE`,
	1 AS `VERSION` 
FROM
	zt_case t1 

	) t1
